Executive Personal Overdraft

The Executive Personal Overdraft facility is an OD line to the executive employees of category A Employers only to enable them meet personal financing needs from time to time.

Features

  • Customer can receive up to 20% of his/her annual salary subject to a maximum of
  • US$10,000 and a minimum of US$1,000
  • Tenor: Up to 180 days

Eligibility

  • Executive employees of Blue Chip companies/category A employers

Benefits

  • Ability to finance emergency needs while still maintaining normal living standards
  • No collateral required
